# Bake the HandPointer overlay JavaScript library into the chromium
# binary as a `std::string_view` accessor.
#
# Adds `components/psyops/hand_pointer.{h,cc}` and registers a new
# `source_set("hand_pointer")` target in `components/psyops/BUILD.gn`.
#
# The JS module attaches itself to `globalThis.psyops.HandPointer` when
# evaluated in a renderer world. Future patches will reference
# `psyops::HandPointerJs()` from a renderer-side hook to inject the
# script on demand; this patch only ships the library bytes.

--- /dev/null
